Package net.canarymod.hook.system

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    LoadWorldHook
    Load World Hook

    Called when a World is loaded and initialized
    PermissionCheckHook
    This hook is called after the PermissionProvider has resolved the permission, to alter the final outcome and eventually temporary allow a permission to a player
    PluginDisableHook
    Called when a plugin is disabled
    PluginEnableHook
    Called when a plugin is enabled.
    ServerGuiStartHook
    Called when a GUI is started
    ServerListPingHook
    Called when a client ping the server
    ServerShutdownHook
    Server shutdown hook.
    ServerTickHook
    Called in the servers tick loop, before world processing.
    UnloadWorldHook
    Called before a world is unloaded.
    Before a world is unloaded, it will be saved! After a world is unloaded it will not be processed in the tick loop anymore.
